\v 11 \x * \xo 3:11 \xt Jo 3:32, 8:26\x*Hi hetput werek. Haiu mat…®p menmen haiu epei merteiyem, haiu mat…®p menmen haiu epei m…®rem. Te yi yeweik…®n sip yewet menmen haiu metpiyem.
